{"word":"H25 - אֲבִי גִבְעֹון - ʼĂbîy Gibʻôwn - ab-ee' ghib-one' - Father of Gibeon","slug":"H25","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<strong>Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">אֲבִי גִבְעֹון</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Transliteration: </strong>ʼĂbîy Gibʻôwn"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Phonetic: </strong>ab-ee' ghib-one'"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Short Definition: </strong>Father of Gibeon"},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<b>&#x05D0;&#x05D1;&#x05D9; &#x05D2;&#x05D1;&#x05E2;&#x05D5;&#x05DF; - 'a&#x0306;b&#x0131;&#x0302;y gib&#x201B;o&#x0302;n</b> - <i>ab-ee' ghib-one'</i><p/>From <a href=\"#/H1\">H1</a> and <a href=\"#/H1391\">H1391</a>; <i>father</i> (that is <i>founder</i>) <i>of Gibon</i>; <i>Abi-Gibon</i>, perhaps an Israelite: - father of Gibeon."},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<strong>Cognate:</strong> <a href=\"#/H1375\">H1375</a>, <a href=\"#/H1387\">H1387</a>, <a href=\"#/H1388\">H1388</a>, <a href=\"#/H1389\">H1389</a>, <a href=\"#/H1390\">H1390</a>, <a href=\"#/H1391\">H1391</a>, <a href=\"#/H1392\">H1392</a>, <a href=\"#/H1393\">H1393</a>, <a href=\"#/H1394\">H1394</a>, <a href=\"#/H1395\">H1395</a>, <a href=\"#/H4021\">H4021</a>"}]}